#, no-c-format
msgid "Matching tiles are such tiles where the face pictograms match exactly."
msgstr "मेलयुक्ताः टाइल्स् तादृशाः टाइल्स् सन्ति यत्र मुखचित्रचित्रं सम्यक् मेलति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168 index.docbook:178 index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "टीका:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are exceptions to this rule. In the traditional game of Mahjong each "
"tile has a matching one except for the <quote>Flowers</quote> and "
"<quote>Seasons</quote> tiles."
msgstr ""
"अस्य नियमस्य अपवादाः सन्ति । महजोङ्गस्य पारम्परिकक्रीडायां प्रत्येकस्य टाइल् इत्यस्य "
"<quote>पुष्पाणि</quote> तथा <quote>ऋतु</quote> टाइल् इत्येतौ विहाय एकः मेलयुक्तः भवति "
"।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Flowers</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Flowers</quote> टाइल्स् इत्यस्य सेट् मध्ये द्विगुणाः नास्ति, तेषां प्रत्यक्षतया परस्परं "
"मेलनं कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Seasons</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"<quote>ऋतुः</quote> टाइल्-समूहे समुच्चये द्विगुणाः नास्ति, तेषां प्रत्यक्षतया परस्परं मेलनं कर्तुं "
"शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tiles can only be removed if they can be connected with a maximum of three "
"connected lines that do not cross any other tile. Lines can be horizontal or "
"vertical, but not diagonal."
msgstr ""
"टाइल्स् केवलं तदा एव निष्कासयितुं शक्यन्ते यदा ते अधिकतमं त्रीणि सम्बद्धरेखाभिः सह संयोजितुं "
"शक्यन्ते ये अन्यं टाइल् न लङ्घयन्ति । रेखाः क्षैतिजः लम्बवत् वा भवितुम् अर्हन्ति, परन्तु तिर्यक् न "
"।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not have to draw the lines by yourself, the game does this for you. "
"Just mark two matching tiles on the board, if they can be connected by a "
"line with at most two bends, the line is drawn and the tiles are removed."
msgstr ""
"भवता स्वयमेव रेखाः आकर्षितुं न प्रयोजनम्, क्रीडा भवतः कृते एतत् करोति। केवलं फलकस्य उपरि "
"द्वौ मेलयुक्तौ टाइल् चिह्नितव्यम्, यदि ते अधिकतमं द्वौ मोचनौ युक्तया रेखायाः माध्यमेन संयोजितुं "
"शक्यन्ते तर्हि रेखा आकृष्यते, टाइल्स् च निष्कासितानि भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines may only cross empty areas of the board."
msgstr "रेखाः केवलं फलकस्य रिक्तक्षेत्राणि एव लङ्घयितुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some games are unsolvable. If you would like to avoid unsolvable games check "
"the option <guilabel>Create solvable games only</guilabel> in the "
"configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"केचन क्रीडाः असमाधानीयाः भवन्ति। यदि भवान् असमाधानीयक्रीडां परिहरितुम् इच्छति तर्हि "
"विन्याससंवादे <guilabel>केवलं समाधानयोग्यं क्रीडां रचयतु</guilabel> इति विकल्पं पश्यतु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scores are awarded for the time the player needs to remove all the tiles "
"from the game board. Games with more tiles give more scores."
msgstr ""
"यदा खिलाडयः क्रीडाफलकात् सर्वाणि टाइल्स् हर्तुं प्रवृत्तः भवति तस्य समयस्य कृते स्कोराः "
"प्रदत्ताः भवन्ति । अधिकानि टाइल्स् युक्ताः क्रीडाः अधिकं स्कोरं ददति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you played with the <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> setting enabled, the "
"score will be doubled."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> सेटिङ्ग् सक्षमं कृत्वा क्रीडति तर्हि स्कोरः "
"द्विगुणः भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be eligible for a place amongst the high scores player has to complete a "
"game instance within the shortest period of time possible."
msgstr ""
"उच्चाङ्कप्राप्तानाम् मध्ये स्थानं प्राप्तुं योग्यतां प्राप्तुं खिलाडयः अल्पतमसमये एव एकं "
"क्रीडादृष्टान्तं सम्पन्नं कर्तव्यं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the player uses the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature "
"the record will not be considered as a high score."
msgstr ""
"यदि खिलाडी <quote>Undo</quote> अथवा <quote>Hint</quote> इति विशेषतायाः उपयोगं "
"करोति तर्हि अभिलेखः उच्चाङ्कः इति न गण्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "संकेता"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on a tile with the &RMB; to highlight all matching tiles on the board. "
"Unlike using the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature, this "
"help is allowed without being considered cheating."
msgstr ""
"&RMB; फलकस्य उपरि सर्वाणि मेलयुक्तानि टाइल्स् प्रकाशयितुं । <quote>Undo</quote> अथवा "
"<quote>Hint</quote> इति विशेषतायाः उपयोगात् विपरीतम्, एषा सहायता वञ्चना इति न "
"मन्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "अन्तरफलक अवलोकन"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "मेनू आइटम"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "गेम मेनू इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Game</guimenu> menu lets you control the status of the current "
"game:"
msgstr "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> मेन्यू वर्तमानक्रीडायाः स्थितिं नियन्त्रयितुं शक्नोति:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu><guimenuitem>नव</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Finishes the current game</action> and starts a new session with new "
"tiles."
msgstr ""
"<action>वर्तमानं क्रीडां समाप्तं करोति</action> नूतन-टाइल्-सहितं नूतनं सत्रं च आरभते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Restart Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>खेलं पुनः आरभत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restarts the current game with the same tiles."
msgstr "वर्तमानक्रीडां समानैः टाइल्-सहितं पुनः आरभते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>विराम</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Pauses the game</action>, especially the timer which affects the "
"scoring. The menu entry is also used for resuming the game."
msgstr ""
"<action>क्रीडां विरामयति</action>, विशेषतः समयनिर्धारकः यः स्कोरिंग् प्रभावितं करोति "
"। मेनू-प्रविष्टिः क्रीडायाः पुनः आरम्भार्थम् अपि उपयुज्यते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu><guimenuitem>उच्चाङ्कान् दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows your top ten charts of &kshisen;."
msgstr "&kshisen; इत्यस्य भवतः शीर्षदश चार्ट्स् दर्शयति।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu><guimenuitem>निवृत्तं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kshisen;."
msgstr "<कर्म>त्यजति</action> &kshisen;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the menu items can also be controlled by keyboard shortcuts. See "
"<xref linkend=\"key-bindings\"/> for a list."
msgstr ""
"केचन मेनू-वस्तूनि कीबोर्ड-शॉर्टकट्-द्वारा अपि नियन्त्रयितुं शक्यन्ते । सूचीं कृते <xref linkend="
"\"key-bindings\"/> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "The Move Menu इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>चल</guimenu><guimenuitem>पूर्ववर्ती</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undoes the last step</action>. Same as the <guibutton>Undo</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<action>अन्तिमपदं पूर्ववर्तयति</action> । साधनपट्ट्यां <guibutton>Undo</guibutton> "
"इति बटन् इव ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>चल</guimenu><guimenuitem>पुनः कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Redoes the last step</action>. Same as the <guibutton>Redo</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<action>अन्तिमपदं पुनः करोति</action> । साधनपट्ट्यां <guibutton>पुनः कुर्वन्तु</"
"guibutton> इति बटन् इव ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>चल</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>संकेत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Shows a hint</action>, which two tiles to remove next."
msgstr "<action>एकं संकेतं दर्शयति</action>, यत् द्वौ टाइलौ अग्रे निष्कासितव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>ध्वनयः वादयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plays a sound when you touch a tile by clicking with it the &LMB; and when a "
"tile is falling down playing with <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> enabled."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवन्तः टाइल् स्पृशन्ति तदा तेन सह &LMB; तथा च यदा <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> "
"सक्षमं कृत्वा क्रीडन् टाइल् अधः पतति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kshisen;…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kshisen;…</guimenuitem> विन्यस्यताम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"configuration\">configuration dialog</link> to "
"change &kshisen; settings."
msgstr ""
"उद्घाटयति<link linkend=\"configuration\"> विन्याससंवादः</link> परिवर्तनं कर्तुं &amp;"
"kshisen; सेटिंग्स् इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kshisen; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &kshisen; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेनु< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

